      "text": "だから、軽くですわよ！\nか・る・く！",
      "startTime": 63.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 64.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "それで『月のテンペスト　可愛い』とか……",
      "startTime": 64.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "『成宮すず　美人』とかで検索したんですの",
      "startTime": 68.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 72.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、いい評判しか出ないはず\n……と思ったのに",
      "startTime": 75.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "嫌なことが書いてあったから落ち込んでたのか？",
      "startTime": 78.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
